title: Total Eclipse of The NFL
itunes:title: Total Eclipse of The NFL
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler & Gregg Rosenthal – recap all the latest news from around the NFL including what the Jaguars might do about Blake Bortles, Patriots rookie Derek Rivers tearing  his ACL, and Ryan Kelly to the boomerang IR list.  The heroes name the players on their “eclipsed” list inspired by the solar eclipse this coming Monday, August 21st.
